Sixteen fecal and 14 nasal swab specimens were collected from cattle showing intestinal and/or respiratory manifestations. The total RNA extracts of these samples were tested with real-time RT-PCR and RT-RPA. Both assays showed the same performance (19 positive and 11 negative cases). The cycle threshold and threshold time values of RT-PCR and RT-RPA respectively well at an R
2 value of 0.8 (Fig. 2
).
